# Subagent Model and AuthType Switching Patch
# 
# This patch enables subagents to switch to their configured model and authType,
# ensuring the correct baseUrl from model providers config is used.
#
# Key changes:
# 1. Save original model/authType before subagent execution
# 2. Convert string authType to AuthType enum
# 3. Look up model config from registry to get baseUrl
# 4. Switch to subagent's model and authType
# 5. Restore original model/authType after completion
#
# Applied: 2026-03-04
